	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Pirates used to turn CNROM games into NROM games by cutting the CHR in half.  They removed the half of the CHR that was only used for the title screen, and maybe also merged the pages if there was anything cut out in the same place on one page but not the other.
<br />
<br />But it sounds like you want to turn an NROM board into a CNROM board... why bother?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


